raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do unlock_gallery_image(\"mabel\", \"1\")
Mabel: Guess who 😎
Player: Hey Mabel
Player: Did you make it to the dorms?
Mabel: Funny you should ask
Mabel: Yes, yes I did
Mabel: Agent007 🕵️
Mabel: Everest, Mabel Everest
Mabel: World's greatest spy has reached the dorm room
- [Play Along] [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: Mabel007, this is HQ
	Player: What's your status? Over.
	Mabel: 😂
	Mabel: HQ this is agent Mabel007
	Mabel: The eagle has landed, I repeat, the eagle has landed
	Mabel: Thought: People would think we're lame but I don't mind being lame when it's with you
- Nice, how's the room?
	Player: Nice, how's the room?
	Mabel: Oh
	Mabel: Thought: Guess he's not in the mood
	Mabel: It's okayish
	Mabel: Small
	Mabel: Very small
	Mabel: sfx: bedcreak2: *creak*
	Mabel: And the bed is loud
	Mabel: Thought: I'm never getting over this bed
Mabel: I can't believe we're actually college students now
Mabel: Like REAL hairy adults
Mabel: Living on our own, doing our own laundry and dishes and scrubbing the toilets
Mabel: The kind of people children fear 👻
Player: Scary huh?
Mabel: SUPER scary
Player: Solo room though right?
Mabel: Yeah thank god
Mabel: I could NOT handle a roommate
Player: What, afraid they'd have a pet tarantula?
Mabel: DON'T EVEN JOKE ABOUT THAT
Mabel: What if they snored??
Mabel: Or had people over all the time??
Mabel: Or what if they were just... weird?
Mabel: Like... weirder than me 😱
- You're perfect the way you are [#love]
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: You're perfect the way you are
	Mabel: Gah! 🥰
	Mabel: Don't flirt with me so suddenly omg
	Mabel: Let me at least catch my breath from all this moving business
	Mabel: PinkThought: Jeez you really know how to treat a girl
	Player: I can't help it! 😘
- I'd be the same honestly
	Player: I'd be the same honestly
	Player: Living with a stranger sounds like anything can go wrong easily
	Mabel: RIGHT??
- Nobody is as weird as you 😂 [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
	Player: That's not even possible
	Player: Nobody is as weird as you 😂
	Mabel: 😒 Meanie
	Player: I'm saying you'd be fine
	Mabel: I guess
	Mabel: Aaanyway
Mabel: I can't believe I had to say bye to Mom
Mabel: Like I never had to LEAVE LEAVE you know what I mean?
Player: I know the feeling
Mabel: She cried
Mabel: I cried
Mabel: It was a whole thing
Player: Aww
Mabel: She kept hugging me and saying \"my baby's all grown up\"
Mabel: I was like MOM PEOPLE ARE WATCHING 😭
Mabel: But I was crying too so it looked so silly
Mabel: Is that lame?
Player: That's cute
Player: You two are close, nothing wrong with that
Mabel: 🥺
Mabel: Thanks
Mabel: Thought: I love that you don't judge me
Mabel: The worst part was saying bye to Ms Whiskers
Mabel: She didn't even look at me when I left LOL
Mabel: She was just hanging out like nothing special was happening
- I'm sure she'll miss you [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: I'm sure she'll miss you
	Mabel: I know but still 😭
- Cats are zero loyalty [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
	Player: Cats are like that 😂 Zero loyalty
	Mabel: Omg don't say that about my baby
Mabel: You remember how silly she was? 🥺
Player: Of course, she doesn't let me anywhere near you 😆
Player: I have battle scars to prove it
Mabel: 😂 She's just protective
Mabel: Thought: She really loved you actually
Mabel: Thought: She would meow at the door when you'd leave
Mabel: Thought: It made me a little jealous
Mabel: Mom promised to send me pictures of her every day 🥹
Mabel: I hope I get to see her soon
Player: I hope so too!
Mabel: I have to start unpacking all these boxes omg
Mabel: Mom packed SO much stuff
Player: Like what?
Mabel: Okay so
Mabel: She packed Mr Buttons
Player: The bear?
Mabel: YES the bear
Mabel: He's been with me since I was like 5
Mabel: I can't sleep without him okay!!
Mabel: Don't judge me plss 🥹
Player: 😂 I didn't even say anything
Mabel: Good 😇
Mabel: She also packed my lucky blanket
Mabel: And like 50 photos
Mabel: And a whole box of snacks \"in case the cafeteria food is bad\"
Player: That's a lot of stuff!
Player: You gonna have room for all that?
Mabel: I'll make it work!
Player: Your mom is precious
Mabel: She really is 🥹
Mabel: Thought: I miss her already
Player: How's the new phone?
Mabel: Omg SOOO helpful!!
Mabel: I was able to sort out stuff on my calendar like a todo list
Mabel: I love Social Scene too
Mabel: I get to see what mom and kitty are up to!
Mabel: Thank you so much ❤️ I love it
Player: I'm glad! 😊
Player: I got one for me too
Mabel: It must have cost you a lot 😭
- It was really nothing [#dollar] [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Day1Money\") == false]
	set PhoneUnlocks.claim = \"Day1Money\"
	Player: It was really nothing
	Player: I have some to spare
	Mabel: Glad to hear that buuut
- It was really nothing [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Day1Money\") == true]
	Player: It was really nothing
	Player: I have some to spare
	Mabel: Glad to hear that buuut
- They weren't cheap for sure
	Player: They weren't cheap for sure
	Player: It was worth it 
Mabel: I feel like I should pay you back for this somehow
Mabel: Is there anything I can do 🥰
Player: There is one thing
Player: My gallery is empty and sad
Mabel: You want a picture?
Mabel: I'm still no good at those
Mabel: Thought: Pictures make me self conscious too
Mabel: Okay, I can do that I think
Mabel: Let me fix my hair first
Player: Take your time
Mabel: It's really messy from the long trip lol
Mabel: Okay done
Mabel: img: mabel/3
Mabel: I look tired don't I? 🙃
Mabel: The drive was seriously long, I fell asleep on the way
Mabel: Thought: So far away from home
- CUTE
	Player: CUTE
	Mabel: 🥺
	Mabel: Thanks ❤️
	Mabel: Thought: I had to fix my hair hehe
- You do look a little tired
	set Story.flag = \"Day1Picture\"
	Player: You do look a little tired
	Player: Make sure you get some good sleep tonight
	Mabel: I do need it 😊
	Mabel: I'll take a better one for you later, promise
	Player: Can't wait!
- What are those boxes behind you
	set Story.flag = \"BoxInvestigation\"
	Player: What's that behind you btw?
	Mabel: Oh the boxes?
	Mabel: They're my stuff I still need to unpack but one of them is FREE STUFF apparently! 🥳
	Mabel: The last girl who lived here left them behind
	Player: Score!?
	Mabel: Right?? I have so much to unpack though so
	Mabel: I'll investigate later
Mabel: Wait so are we in the same dorm building or what?
Mabel: Can you come by?
Player: Sure, just give me 45 minutes
Mabel: Whaaat 😭
Mabel: That's SO far
Mabel: I thought we'd be like... neighbors again 😭
Player: Different campuses Mabes 😔
Mabel: I KNOW but still
Mabel: When am I gonna see you?
Player: I'll come by though eventually, don't worry
Player: I need to figure out the bus schedule once they start running
Mabel: Promise?
- I promise [#love] [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: I promise
	Player: We'll make it work ❤️
	Mabel: ❤️
	Mabel: Thought: I believe you
	Mabel: Okay that makes me feel better
- Yeah for sure [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
	Player: Yeah for sure
	Mabel: Thought: Was that a promise?
	Mabel: Okie dokes
Mabel: It's just weird you know?
Mabel: We've always been close by
Mabel: Now I can't even see you whenever
Player: We'll make it work
Player: Don't let it bring you down
Mabel: Yeah
Mabel: Yeah you're right
Mabel: Thought: I hope so
Mabel: Okay I should probably start unpacking
Mabel: It's gonna take a while
Mabel: Then I need to go explore a bit
Mabel: See where everything is like the grocery store
Mabel: Before it gets dark
Player: Good idea!
Mabel: 😊
Mabel: Hey
Mabel: Thanks for being here
Mabel: Even if it's just through the phone for now
Mabel: It helps
- I'm always here for you [#love]
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: I'm always here for you
	Player: You know that right?
	Mabel: I know ❤️
	Mabel: PinkThought: Seriously giving me goosebumps
- No problem
	Player: No problem
	Mabel: 😊
Mabel: Okay agent Mabel signing out 😉
Mabel: Talk later alligator 🐊
Player: Later Mabes
Mabel: 😘
do social_post(\"collegelife_intro\")
do social_post(\"suzanna_new_semester\")
do queue_social_post(\"mabel_intro\")
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
